Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_2.Text: Meet with the king in Aliahan Castle.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_4.Text: Place all of the orbs on their pedestals.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_5.Text: Pay a visit to the house in Reeve with a red door.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_6.Text: Go to the eastern spring and access the teleportal.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_7.Text: Make your way through the Path of Promise.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_9.Text: Pass through the outpost and head to Portoga.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_10.Text: Find some black pepper to trade for a ship.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_11.Text: Give the black pepper to the king of Portoga.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_12.Text: Find the castle from your dream.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_13.Text: Travel far and wide in search of the orbs.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_14.Text: Explore the depths of Gaia's Navel.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_15.Text: Find Baramos within his lair and defeat him.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_16.Text: Inform the king that Baramos is no more.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_17.Text: Kill some time until you begin to feel sleepy.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_18.Text: Work out how to reach Zoma's Citadel.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_21.Text: Report to the king of Tantegel.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_22.Text: Explore the Castle of the Dragon Queen.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Main_23.Text: Head to the cave to the east of Baramos's Lair.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_1.Text: Track down an infamous thief in one of the world's towers.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_2.Text: Head to the pyramid and find the magic key.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_3.Text: Find Nordy the dwarf and head east.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_5.Text: Pay a visit to Gopal's shop in Baharata.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_6.Text: Slay the monster in the cave to the east of Jipang.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_8.Text: Learn the king of Manoza's secret.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_10.Text: Find the elderly man who seeks a magical staff.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_12.Text: Find a sword of the earth and a fiery mountain.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_14.Text: Introduce a merchant to the old man east of Persistence.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_15.Text: Check in on the merchant as <IfGender_MERCHANT(he helps,she helps,they help)> to build up the town.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_17.Text: See what's behind the chair in {MERCHANT}'s mansion.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_21.Text: Head to the tower to the north and free Rubiss.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_22.Text: Go to the Sanctum and find the Rainbow Drop.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_23.Text: Take the Rainbow Drop to the cape north-west of Rimuldar.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_24.Text: Sneak into Manoza Castle after nightfall.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_26.Text: Cross the fields south of Reeve and head to the Dreamer's Tower.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_27.Text: Find the old man in the Dreamer's Tower.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_29.Text: Pick up some black pepper at Alltrades Abbey.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_31.Text: Use some Fading Jenny and sneak into Edina.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_32.Text: Use the bottomless pot by the reef to the north of Mur.

Txt_Map_Test_Guide_Sub_33.Text: Follow the path created by the volcanic eruption.
